ily loads or burdens): </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n104119.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> abs., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hold out, endure, be patient, submit</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἤτοι ἐγὼ μενέω καὶ τλήσομαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.317</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.308</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔτι τλαίης ἐνιαυτόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:288\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.288</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:219\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.219</biblScope> </bibl>; esp. in imper., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τέτλαθι, μῆτερ ἐμή, καὶ ἀνάσχεο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:586\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.586</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τλῆτε, φίλοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:299\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.299</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τέτλαθι δή, κραδίη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\